reviewText: My child loves Dora. Any Dora is her favorite as long add she has a new one to watch every time I can afford one.

Another great Dora DVD!  This one-hour long Dora DVD features three episodes filled with fun and adventure of Dora and her friends.  Yes they are episodes that your child may have seen on television already but it is nice to have them all on one DVD and perfect for those times when your child wants to watch Dora but she is not on.  My 2 year old absolutely loves Dora and would watch this DVD on repeat if I let her!  She teaches great lessons, a few Spanish words and its just a wholesome show.

Episodes include:

Dora's Great Roller Skate Adventure
Check-Up Day
School Science Fair
I got this for my little girl and she loves it and so do I. It's very educational and funny. Well worth the money!

My girls love Dora the Explorer. This DVD contains three episodes from the Nick Jr. cartoon. Amazon doesn't always do a good job on their DVD episode listings so here are the episodes that are included on this DVD:

1. Dora's Great Roller Skate Adventure - Dora and Boots want to go to a skate park, but it is closed by a bully.
2. Check-Up Day - Dora goes for her annual check-up.
3. School Science Fair - Dora and her friend make a volcano for the school science fair.
One of my 4 yr old daughter's favorite Dora movies!
